    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3030470/extras/104a7f8f632422149acbf673bd76e71b.avif?t=1769021598\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3030470/extras_big/104a7f8f632422149acbf673bd76e71b.avif?t=1769021598 width=800 height=54 /></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Discover the fractured world of <i><strong>You Belong in the Stars</strong></i>, where you travel from solar system to solar system in an open world galaxy, exploring things and stuff</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3030470/extras/fedea23d35110800b278255a0f7a1581.poster.avif?t=1769021598\" width=800 height=262 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3030470/extras/fedea23d35110800b278255a0f7a1581.webm?t=1769021598\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3030470/extras/fedea23d35110800b278255a0f7a1581.mp4?t=1769021598\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3030470/extras/068426c243b642f6b911aaaf1005e07a.avif?t=1769021598\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3030470/extras_big/068426c243b642f6b911aaaf1005e07a.avif?t=1769021598 width=800 height=54 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3030470/extras/b22be81d86b9d3d5c0eb8b59f5b37ab4.poster.avif?t=1769021598\" width=800 height=262 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3030470/extras/b22be81d86b9d3d5c0eb8b59f5b37ab4.webm?t=1769021598\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3030470/extras/b22be81d86b9d3d5c0eb8b59f5b37ab4.mp4?t=1769021598\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Engage in dogfights with smaller spacecraft or pilot larger cruisers. Choose from a wide selection of ships, each with unique combat abilities and utilities to attack, defend, or even exit your ship to fight enemies inside space stations or other vessels.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3030470/extras/ac0bdac88db908e6eb3f27ac5d9ffa6c.poster.avif?t=1769021598\" width=800 height=262 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3030470/extras/ac0bdac88db908e6eb3f27ac5d9ffa6c.webm?t=1769021598\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3030470/extras/ac0bdac88db908e6eb3f27ac5d9ffa6c.mp4?t=1769021598\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3030470/extras/ff08c4613b091bcb188b08fcc35ff57c.avif?t=1769021598\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3030470/extras_big/ff08c4613b091bcb188b08fcc35ff57c.avif?t=1769021598 width=800 height=54 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Completing quests earns you money to spend on ships and equipment, while also improving your reputation with the quest-giving organization. Meanwhile, your target’s opinion of you worsens, eventually forcing them to take action against you. The reputation system in <i>You Belong in the Stars</i> determines whether organizations will be friendly or hostile towards you and others.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3030470/extras/cba5aee0d08f8324b4953a44237615d7.poster.avif?t=1769021598\" width=800 height=262 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3030470/extras/cba5aee0d08f8324b4953a44237615d7.webm?t=1769021598\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3030470/extras/cba5aee0d08f8324b4953a44237615d7.mp4?t=1769021598\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3030470/extras/4232c93b6aff07fa49dc123f2ef846a1.avif?t=1769021598\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3030470/extras_big/4232c93b6aff07fa49dc123f2ef846a1.avif?t=1769021598 width=800 height=54 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>You Belong in the Stars</i> gives you the freedom to explore its vast solar and star systems, but traveling between them is no simple task. Or maybe it will be I didnt decide yet</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3030470/extras/c26c48ad70de1f3bca44cded14218aa3.poster.avif?t=1769021598\" width=800 height=262 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3030470/extras/c26c48ad70de1f3bca44cded14218aa3.webm?t=1769021598\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3030470/extras/c26c48ad70de1f3bca44cded14218aa3.mp4?t=1769021598\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3030470/extras/35f50329389bfd50b413cdf7cbc2a564.avif?t=1769021598\" data-big-src=https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3030470/extras_big/35f50329389bfd50b413cdf7cbc2a564.avif?t=1769021598 width=800 height=54 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The early access wont feature all of these, but the final release will:</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > 50+ unique ships drawn by Delu</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Some of these ships have walkable interiors that you can seamlessly enter and exit on foot or in a vehicle that fits through the doors</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >10+ origins, most of them unlockable after achieving certain feats in the campaign</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >a large amount and variety of quests:</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >dogfighting</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >securing locations through a shootout outside of your ship</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Saving friendly ships in emergencies</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >boss fights</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >some special quests that won't fit these categories </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >mining</p></li></ul></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >10+ different solar systems with various orgs, locations and events in them</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >more cute anime girls</p></li></ul>",
